  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d659aa9d-a9ff-4046-8f9b-106cadd76e8c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a747b353-a4b2-48f9-a6e7-bacb1916d98d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f89d57a9-e0bc-4fce-b635-655276ab1c93\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>캘린더(달력), 1년 홍보물의 꽃 캘린더</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e350f17-a853-4679-a2d5-9020c53e4aac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-b1966c30-01ff-4e70-98d8-fcd56164bfdc\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-826942c0-be18-48f2-a6d0-e67e538b5459\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">인쇄 사장에서 연말에 가장 바쁘고 주문이 많은 홍보물 중에 하나가 캘린더와 다이어리 시장입니다. 캘린더, 즉 달력은 인쇄물 소비의 주요 홍보 매체로서 오래되고 전통있는 시장 중에 하나입니다. 시계가 실용적인 측면에서 탈피하여 멋과 악세서리 시장으로 변화하듯이 캘린더 시장 또한 옛날같지 않지만 소량 다품종 디지털로 전환으로 기본 1부서부터 몇 만부에 이르기까지 다양한 시장을 형성 중에 있습니다. 오늘은 기본적으로 캘린더의 구성과 주문에 대해 알아보도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-2c0960e0-0281-4d66-b511-37c60863829d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b73ee65b-7472-4bef-b2b2-eb00968b3178\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-69d8e2b8-618f-4400-ba0e-a00633dde64a\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222938773096/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222938773096/001.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222938773096/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222938773096/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90b8cab2-7ee0-41c7-840e-5f551fa760df\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-58e3d2b8-3aea-4140-891d-f3411db4b415\" style=\"\">기본적인 캘린더 사진</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a71c3e3b-e683-43ad-8b9a-968ae132f3da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-a51d4ebf-8b1f-4201-8ec7-ce88c9b890c5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222938773096/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-60a32aef-87c9-45a7-9ffb-d15edcf96c66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3dd5b720-c1cc-46c0-85d0-2aa4b0a9b488\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기본 분류</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbef48ed-a07b-43f5-9394-135facfde50e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9eb41135-c029-4899-a366-9260190ad562\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">캘린더(달력)는 크게 두가지 형태로 나뉩니다. 하나는 벽걸이형이고 또 다른 하나는 탁상용입니다. 벽걸이형은 벽에 걸 수 있도록 스프링이나 링으로 제본이 되어있는 형태이고 탁상용은 책상 위에 올려 놓을 수 있도록 삼각대로 이루어진 형태입니다. 요즘은 거의 탁상용으로 주문이 많이 이루어 지며 음식점이나 요식 업종에서 주로 벽걸이용으로 주문이 많이 이루어지는 상황입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2f76781b-c970-4933-86a6-583b7644830d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0860f989-4e0e-4ee6-b9f5-da18e5673af1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03bb148a-f7d2-4bc9-85c6-d81adc1d7e4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-61357154-ddd6-4efe-8196-a55e7461806b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-9f617cd8-9b41-44ba-9f91-d65b57a63b4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" c